@baseUrl = http://localhost:5121/api

### Test Invoice Search - All Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Invoice Search - With Status Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?status=Sent
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Invoice Search - With Search Term
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?search=test
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Invoice Search - With Hebrew Search Term
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?search=חשבונית
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Invoice Search - With Invoice Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?search=INV
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Invoice Search - Combined (Status + Search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?status=Sent&search=test
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Single Invoice by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/1
Content-Type: application/json
